						<summary>

						<p>Pāṇḍya, Vīrapāṇḍya, 9th year = A.D. 1305.</p>						

						<p>Records the building of the kitchen by Udayaṉ Bhuvanasiṅgadēva for the merit of his overlord Chēmappiḷḷaiyār between the 17th day of Māsi of the 9th year and Āṉi of the 10th year, that is within a period of five months.</p>						

